HEADWORD: Coquettish
<hw>Co*quet"tish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Practicing or
exhibiting coquetry; alluring; enticing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A pretty, <qex>coquettish</qex> housemaid.</q> <rj><qau>W.
